==制作==
剧组邀请了《[[超凡蜘蛛侠|超凡蜘蛛侠]]》团队协助拍摄。

片中[[青马大桥|青马大桥]]只有17分钟，但是剧组拍摄了100多天。甄子丹和王宝强的大雪纷飞情景打斗戏在中朝边境[[长白山|长白山]]拍摄。甄子丹的[[巴士|双层巴士车]][[轻功|轻功]]戏非常逼真。<ref>{{cite news |author= |url=http://ent.163.com/13/0225/15/8OIN3JPG000300B1.html |title=《3D冰封侠》曝剧照 甄子丹不惧危险拍高难场景 |newspaper=网易 |date=2013-02-25 |language=zh-hans |location= |accessdate=2014-12-20 |archive-date=2014-12-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141220110915/http://ent.163.com/13/0225/15/8OIN3JPG000300B1.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|author=|url=http://ent.xinmin.cn/2012/12/19/17724730.html|title=王宝强《冰封侠》和甄子丹从头打到尾|newspaper=新民网|date=2012-12-19|language=zh-hans|location=|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141220110617/http://ent.xinmin.cn/2012/12/19/17724730.html|archivedate=2014-12-20|accessdate=2014-12-20}}</ref>

